    <section class="home-body">
        <p>
            Hi! I'm Nathan, and welcome to a little window into my programming world.
        </p>
        <p style="display: inline-block">
            Professionally, I use .NET (C# and VB) and SQL Server in my role maintaining and developing a wide array of backend systems for
            <a href="https://www.reyrey.co.uk/Claro.html">Claro (Contact Advantage)</a> and various other internal and 3rd party services.
            I also have lots of experience with COBOL developing <a href="https://www.reyrey.co.uk/POWER-DMS.html">POWER DMS</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
            In my spare time I also enjoy coding, and I have a passion for low-level development. You'll usually find me using C++ or C# in my personal projects.
            I'm also a big fan of music, being a bass guitar player, as well as cricket and F1. I love to try and find ways to mix my passion for coding with my other hobbies.
        </p>
    </section>
</article>